## File Map

| File | Responsibility |
|------|---------------|
| `go.mod` | Module definition — go 1.26, all dependencies |
| `internal/models/models.go` | GORM model structs for all 5 tables |
| `internal/db/db.go` | `Connect()` — GORM open + pool config + AutoMigrate |
| `internal/apierror/apierror.go` | `Sanitize(err)` — strips SQL using lib/pq PgError |
| `internal/auth/token.go` | JWT issue/validate (no prefix), bcrypt, GenerateToken |
| `internal/email/service.go` | Plunk track event client — env-var template IDs |
| `internal/middleware/auth.go` | `RequireAuth` reads `Authorization: Bearer` header |
| `internal/auth/handler.go` | 9 auth HTTP handlers — GORM queries, JSON responses only |
| `internal/projects/handler.go` | Project CRUD + file handlers — GORM queries |
| `cmd/server/main.go` | Wire everything, chi router under `/v1/` |
| `internal/billing/handler.go` | Stripe checkout, billing portal, subscription status handlers |
| `internal/billing/webhook.go` | Stripe webhook — subscription lifecycle events |

